The asteroid parts of Starstomp were greatly reacting to the CR chamber. In 
no time, she was repaired. As she exited, she tried to find her way around. 
She entered a room where many computers and monitors were located. One 
holoprojection showed the current state of the battle. She saw Nightlight 
and Termitron as well as many other bots, but it seemed the Chivtrons were 
on the losing side...

Starstomp:
By Prime! This can't be! Alright! I'm going in! (she opened her com) To any 
Chivtron personnel, I'm Starstomp and I am ready to assist if you'd just 
tell me how to get the salg out of this base!

She transformed to her beast mode, ready to trample.
